{
  "stem": "16571.2",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 268.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they used to every now and then bring stale bread and stale cakes to us when-- to Block 8, and we used to have a good-- a good going over once a month or whatever it was, because we used to receive parcels from Switzerland and all these places, the German-- the German Jews.",
      "word_count": 55
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I remember a funny thing.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "One-- once before Christmas, we were taken, a few of us, to arrange chairs.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And the German Jewish prisoners were putting on a show for the officers.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And whilst we was there-- first time I've seen a show.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "First time I've-- I never-- didn't know such a thing existed.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And obviously, it was like a farce like they have today.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And they put on a show.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And they were all clapping away and everything.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "It was to me at that time-- you know, as I said, people were suffering very, very bad, very hard work, and all the rest.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And I was-- for some reason or other, I was chosen-- I was the lucky one.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I just carried the food twice a day from the kitchens, which was about three quarter-- half a mile, three quarter a mile from our blockade.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And in that respect, if you work with food, a little bit rubs on a-- on you.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And you're not as short as people who have been hard working for 8, 10, 12 hours a day.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Just loafing around.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We were-- we were playing [GERMAN].",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We were playing-- I mean, I tried to learn chess because that is-- that was just-- there was about 20 of us, two dozen maybe, who were just assigned for this job.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we were just more or less doing nothing.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
